Package: missingmed
Type: Package
Title: Mediation Analysis with Multiple Imputation for Missing Data
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2024-11-16
Authors@R: person("Davood", "Tofighi",
        email = "dtofighi@gmail.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        comment= c(ORCID= "0000-0001-8523-7776")
        )
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0),
    methods (>= 4.1.0)
